[Checks and Counters]

<p>Despite the effect that Metang has on a battle when it enters the field, it is not without its flaws. Perhaps the most crippling of these is that if your opponent manages to contain their laughter and keep playing the battle, you're basically playing with one Pokemon down. Aside from everything, the best counter to Metang is in fact, another Metang! Metang loses to everything, including itself, so keep that in mind when you are using it.</p>

